<p>人生无常。我已请求<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609937407" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;">RockTeethMothEyes</a></span>，在我超过一年没有活动的情况下，对我的文章的授权、联动、删除等危机情况进行管理。如果我整整三年没有进行活动，我的文章与情节将委托给<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609937407" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;">RockTeethMothEyes</a></span>，但是合著作品所有权归属于它们相应的合著者。如果我从wiki上消失后需要联系我，找<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4598089); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4598089&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609937407" alt="aismallard" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4598089)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4598089); return false;">aismallard</a></span>要我的电话号码。当然这种事情还是别发生的好。</p>
